From Jerry Kaufman Subject Re prayers and advice requested on family problem Cloak yourself in God's sustaining and abiding Pray pray Pray for your brother that he will assume the Godly role that is Pray for your sister in law the what ever is driving her to separate your brother and herself from the the rest of the family will be Pray for God to give you the peace in the knowledge that you may not be able to 'fix' From your description it would appear that it will require devine intervention and the realization by your brother as to what his responsibilities Seek Godly counsel from your pastor or other spiritually mature Know always that He is akways there as a conforter and will give you wisdon and direction as you call on